  "translations": {
    "en": "6. He said: Abu Ja’far Muhammad ibn ‘Ali ibn al-Husayn reported from his father, from Muhammad ibn Yahya al-‘Attar, from Muhammad ibn Ahmad ibn Yahya, from al-Hasan ibn ‘Ali al-Kufi, from al-‘Abbas ibn ‘Amir al-Qasbani, from Ahmad ibn Rizq al-Ghamshani, from Yahya ibn Abi al-‘Ala’, from Jabir, from Abu Ja’far Muhammad ibn ‘Ali, from his father, from his grandfather, peace be upon them, who said: The Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him and his family, said:",
    "ur": "رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وآلہ وسلم نے فرمایا:",
    "tr": "Resûlullah sallâllahu aleyhi ve âlihi ve sellem buyurdu:",
    "fa": "رسول الله صلی الله علیه وآله وسلم فرمود:",
    "id": "Rasulullah shallallahu alaihi wa alihi wa sallam bersabda:",
    "bn": "রাসূলুল্লাহ সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়া আলিহি ওয়া সাল্লাম বলেছেন:",
    "es": "El Mensajero de Al-láh dijo:",
    "fr": "Le Messager d’Allah a dit :",
    "de": "Der Gesandte Allahs sagte:",
    "ru": "Посланник Аллаха сказал:",
    "zh": "真主的使者说:"
  }
}